Feature: Test json inspection payload
    In order to verify my json response
    As a developper
    I want to be able to check json node content

    Background: load JSON
        When I load JSON:
            """
            {
                "foo": "bar",
                "foofoo": true,
                "fooint": 1337,
                "foos": [
                    {"foo": "bar"},
                    {"foo2": "bar2"}
                ],
                "fooo": {
                    "foo": "bar"
                }
            }
            """

